Provide clear inputs: fields, types, validation rules, layout hints, and fictional sample values. Keep prompts concise and include helper text.

3
00:00:18,000 --> 00:00:28,000
Flow: generate the UI mock, export, review for accessibility and security, then map to Pega views or sections in App Studio.

4
00:00:28,000 --> 00:00:38,000
Safety: no real data, check accessibility, align to design system, validate masks and error states. Treat generated code as a reference, not production.

5
00:00:38,000 --> 00:00:50,000
Mapping: document what to rebuild in Pega, keep reusable prompts for intake, review, and approvals, and log prompts and outputs.

